        approach: 'Two facts. (1) If total gas >= total cost the answer exists and is unique. (2) If the running tank goes negative at index i starting from s, no index in [s..i] can complete the loop — the negative was inevitable from somewhere in there. Skip ahead to i+1 and zero the tank. The final start survives every reset, so it must work.',
