        code: `class Solution:
    def romanToInt(self, s):
        v = {'I':1,'V':5,'X':10,'L':50,'C':100,'D':500,'M':1000}
        result = 0
        for i, c in enumerate(s):
            if i + 1 < len(s) and v[c] < v[s[i+1]]:
                result -= v[c]
            else:
                result += v[c]
        return result`,
