        code: `class Solution:
    def minimumAbsoluteDifference(self, arr):
        arr.sort()
        min_diff = min(arr[i+1] - arr[i] for i in range(len(arr) - 1))
        return [[arr[i], arr[i+1]] for i in range(len(arr) - 1) if arr[i+1] - arr[i] == min_diff]`,
