        code: `class Solution:
    def totalFruit(self, fruits):
        from collections import defaultdict
        counts = defaultdict(int)
        l, best = 0, 0
        for r, x in enumerate(fruits):
            counts[x] += 1
            while len(counts) > 2:
                counts[fruits[l]] -= 1
                if counts[fruits[l]] == 0:
                    del counts[fruits[l]]
                l += 1
            best = max(best, r - l + 1)
        return best`,
