        code: `from collections import deque
class Solution:
    def levelOrder(self, root):
        if not root: return []
        result = []
        q = deque([root])
        while q:
            level = []
            for _ in range(len(q)):
                node = q.popleft()
                level.append(node.val)
                for c in node.children:
                    q.append(c)
            result.append(level)
        return result`,
